Rama absent from 1860 Munich for several weeks
1860 Munich must do without attacking midfielder Valdet Rama for about a month.
An examination revealed that the 27-year-old has suffered an adductor injury, the club revealed.
Rama had complained of pain at the beginning of the week.
According to the Munich Lions, the diagnosis means "probably a four week compulsory break".
"It's hit us hard. Rama is a bitter loss."
